\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Of course. This is a critical process, as the integrity of KB-7 and all downstream services depends on a robust, auditable, and repeatable ETL workflow for ingesting foundational knowledge.
\f1\fs24 \cf0 \strokec3 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 \strokec2 Based on the provided context and a review of the principles in the cited sources, here is a detailed, implementation-focused deep dive into the ETL workflow for populating KB-7 with standard clinical ontologies, tailored for your specific use case.
\f1\fs24 \cf0 \strokec3 \
\
